Introduction
------------
The Guanxi Common module provides shared services to the other Guanxi modules
such as the Identity Provider and Service Provider. It's also a useful Java
toolkit for various things such as custom SSL handling and crytopgraphy.

Building
--------
git clone http://github.com/guanxi/guanxi-core.git
git clone http://github.com/guanxi/guanxi-beans.git
git clone http://github.com/guanxi/guanxi-common.git
cd guanxi-common
mvn clean install

More information
----------------
The Guanxi blog: http://codebrane.com/blog/?cat=2

